left_text: S1 with large ventral projection; margin of T6 acutely angled laterally; ﬂagellum modiﬁed
right_text: S1 without ventral projection; margin of T6 not acutely angled laterally; ﬂagellum not modiﬁed

left_text: Gena with elongate lateroventral fovea or crease; distal ﬂagellar segments stout (palearctic)
right_text: Gena without lateroventral fovea; distal ﬂagellar segments, except the last, threadlike (Burma)

left_text: T6 in dorsal view with strongly projecting median lobe; pronotal lobe not carinate; S2 with median longitudinal line of short, appressed hairs, these quite different from long, erect hairs of adjacent areas (Mediterranean region, western nearctic)
right_text: T6 in dorsal view with weakly projecting median lobe; pronotal lobe carinate; S2 without median longitudinal line of short hairs (Mediterranean region)
